<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Due to the fact that linux has case sensitive paths, i cannot load ZendServer_ShMem.</p>

<p>In Zend_Cache::__makeBackend_ there is a call to Zend_Cache::__normalizeName_.
In Zend_Cache::__normalizeName_ the capital M in ShMem is lost. This causes that the right file cannot be loaded.</p>

